GYROMEZES SITE V5

Static website ready for Netlify.

How to deploy:
1. Unzip gyromezes_site_v5.zip.
2. Upload/drag the full folder gyromezes_site_v5 to Netlify.
3. Do not upload only index.html. Do not upload the zip file directly.

Files:
- index.html
- assets/ logo, hero, storefront and signature images

No build command needed.
Publish directory: root folder containing index.html.
